# beginSeekingBackward()

**Instance Method**

Begins seeking backward through the music content.

## Declaration

```swift
func beginSeekingBackward()
```

## Discussion

Use this method to move the current playback position backward in time at an accelerated rate. Seeking begins when you call this method, and continues until you call the [doc://com.apple.MusicKit/documentation/MusicKit/MusicPlayer/endSeeking()] method.

If the player is streaming the underlying content, this method has no effect.
